==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water vine
<hw>Wa"ter vine`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Any plant of
the genus <gen>Phytocrene</gen>, climbing shrubs of Asia and Africa, the
stems of which are singularly porous, and when cut stream with a limpid
potable juice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water violet</ent>⟦br⟧
